      "review_summary": "The branch stacks on the Crabline Slack QA PR, bumps `@openclaw/crabline` from `0.1.3` to `0.1.4`, and adds WhatsApp Crabline transport tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +446, Tests +333, Config 0, Other +9. Total +788 across 45 files.\n\nReproducibility: not applicable. this is a QA Lab feature PR rather than a reported current-main bug. Source and dependency inspection show it adds WhatsApp Crabline contract coverage on top of the open base PR's transport env forwarding.",
